{"tid":1642493,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[風向撚/休息撚出沒注意] 今次佢地用區選做藉口","createTime":"2019-10-09T17:31:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-10T01:41:10.000Z","uid":211469,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2f63f781a8a99c82dcd7dfc0006316fa18d72a73","tid":1642493,"uid":211469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T17:31:30.000Z","msg":"風向撫、休息撚有既定模式，就係<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">睇準我地重視嘅野，然後spin到「前線退場」，總之乜柒都好，最終結論都係勇武退場</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n重視人權法呀?驚美國唔pass呀，勇武退場<br />\n<br />\n驚前線送頭呀? 勇武退場<br />\n<br />\n驚民意逆轉呀?勇武退場<br />\n<br />\n文宣追唔切、補位唔夠快呀?勇武退場／休息<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">總之，千錯萬錯都係勇武嘅錯，勇武退場就可以解決一切問題</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n而家風向撚／休息撚最新話題就係區選，大意就係驚政府搞區選，所以結論仍然係前線唔好出。<br />\n<br />\nTG group已經吹緊風，懇請大家意志一定要堅定，唔好咁易俾呢Ｄ休息撚影響到，仲有就係一見到類似言論即屌，絕對不要留手！！！<br />\n<br />\n亦都請緊記，<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">任何人意圖指揮勇武、代勇武決定停定出，或者果Ｄ「叫人出就係鬼」嘅post，請大家大力屌，以正視聽！！！</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"10cc98780c389fc3b997e8c483a0b1d1839d64b0","tid":1642493,"uid":37525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T18:39:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"45d0313281fd738da72010dc4a975e565fde8842","tid":1642493,"uid":43204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T18:40:59.000Z","msg":"我同意<br />\n但都同意休息埋今個weekend"},{"pid":"8f4a28d6f304dc25cd85c2e26016a5688ed9df2d","tid":1642493,"uid":117040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T01:41:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4KGkzmk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4KGkzmk.jpg&h=4b48d133&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n講區選唔一定喺風向撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港人，所有香港事都要關心！<br />\n不分和勇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />兄弟各自爬山<br />\n<br />\n有個好有心嘅手足針對今屆區選做咗個網站，記錄哂所有現任議員/即將參選嘅社區人士資料，包括區會會議記錄、FB言論、媒體報導等等，好需要大家支持！仲記唔記得運動初期大家都不停叫人登記做選民，用自己能力改變香港，改變議會嘅生態，今年更加選民登記冊共載有413.2萬選民，係創歷年新高！各位巴打絲打手足一齊幫忙提交資料同宣傳！不論今次區選會唔會押後都好，各位有票嘅香港人都要岀嚟行使你嘅公民權利<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">本土戰線都要做呀！</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">選區事實處：<br />\n<a href=\"https://hkfactcheck.io\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkfactcheck.io&d=FZDcFY5BXo0CBgddFpFX552AEL7eB1GKmMTTK1c2%2F04%3D&h=1128b2f8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hkfactcheck.io</a></span></strong><br />\n可以透過公眾提交自己嗰區嘅資料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/10/10/094012_13a56761757811cc12013d0049fd7d8f.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F10%2F10%2F094012_13a56761757811cc12013d0049fd7d8f.jpeg&h=d29e8781&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}